{"surah":101,"verses":[{"n":1,"key":"101:1","arabic":" ٱلْقَارِعَةُ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"The Striking Calamity -","id":"Hari Kiamat,","words":[{"a":"ٱلْقَارِعَةُ","en":"The Striking Calamity","id":"hari kiamat"}]},{"n":2,"key":"101:2","arabic":"مَا ٱلْقَارِعَةُ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"What is the Striking Calamity?","id":"Apakah hari Kiamat itu?","words":[{"a":"مَا","en":"What","id":"apakah"},{"a":"ٱلْقَارِعَةُ","en":"(is) the Striking Calamity","id":"hari kiamat"}]},{"n":3,"key":"101:3","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلْقَارِعَةُ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"And what can make you know what is the Striking Calamity?","id":"Dan tahukah kamu apakah hari Kiamat itu?","words":[{"a":"وَمَآ","en":"And what","id":"dan apakah"},{"a":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","en":"will make you know","id":"kamu tahu"},{"a":"مَا","en":"what","id":"apa"},{"a":"ٱلْقَارِعَةُ","en":"(is) the Striking Calamity","id":"hari kiamat"}]},{"n":4,"key":"101:4","arabic":"يَوْمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلْفَرَاشِ ٱلْمَبْثُوثِ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"It is the Day when people will be like moths, dispersed,","id":"Pada hari itu manusia seperti laron yang beterbangan,","words":[{"a":"يَوْمَ","en":"(The) Day","id":"hari"},{"a":"يَكُونُ","en":"will be","id":"adalah"},{"a":"ٱلنَّاسُ","en":"the mankind","id":"manusia"},{"a":"كَٱلْفَرَاشِ","en":"like moths","id":"seperti anai-anai"},{"a":"ٱلْمَبْثُوثِ","en":"scattered","id":"bertebaran"}]},{"n":5,"key":"101:5","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلْجِبَالُ كَٱلْعِهْنِ ٱلْمَنفُوشِ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"And the mountains will be like wool, fluffed up.","id":"dan gunung-gunung seperti bulu yang dihambur-hamburkan.","words":[{"a":"وَتَكُونُ","en":"And will be","id":"dan adalah"},{"a":"ٱلْجِبَالُ","en":"the mountains","id":"gunung-gunung"},{"a":"كَٱلْعِهْنِ","en":"like wool","id":"seperti bulu"},{"a":"ٱلْمَنفُوشِ","en":"fluffed up","id":"dihambur-hamburkan"}]},{"n":6,"key":"101:6","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"Then as for one whose scales are heavy [with good deeds],","id":"Maka adapun orang yang berat timbangan (kebaikan)nya,","words":[{"a":"فَأَمَّا","en":"Then as for","id":"maka adapun"},{"a":"مَن","en":"(him) whose","id":"siapa/orang"},{"a":"ثَقُلَتْ","en":"(are) heavy","id":"berat"},{"a":"مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","en":"his scales","id":"timbangannya"}]},{"n":7,"key":"101:7","arabic":"فَهُوَ فِى عِيشَةٍ رَّاضِيَةٍ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"He will be in a pleasant life.","id":"maka dia berada dalam kehidupan yang memuaskan (senang).","words":[{"a":"فَهُوَ","en":"Then he","id":"maka dia"},{"a":"فِى","en":"(will be) in","id":"dalam"},{"a":"عِيشَةٍۢ","en":"a life","id":"kehidupan"},{"a":"رَّاضِيَةٍۢ","en":"pleasant","id":"memuaskan"}]},{"n":8,"key":"101:8","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"But as for one whose scales are light,","id":"Dan adapun orang yang ringan timbangan (kebaikan)nya,","words":[{"a":"وَأَمَّا","en":"But as for","id":"dan adapun"},{"a":"مَنْ","en":"(him) whose","id":"orang"},{"a":"خَفَّتْ","en":"(are) light","id":"ringan"},{"a":"مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","en":"his scales","id":"timbangannya"}]},{"n":9,"key":"101:9","arabic":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٌ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"His refuge will be an abyss.","id":"maka tempat kembalinya adalah neraka Hāwiyah.","words":[{"a":"فَأُمُّهُۥ","en":"His abode","id":"maka tempat kembalinya"},{"a":"هَاوِيَةٌۭ","en":"(will be the) Pit","id":"jurang yang dalam/neraka Hawiyah"}]},{"n":10,"key":"101:10","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهْ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"And what can make you know what that is?","id":"Dan tahukah kamu apakah neraka Hāwiyah itu?","words":[{"a":"وَمَآ","en":"And what","id":"dan apakah"},{"a":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","en":"will make you know","id":"kamu tahu"},{"a":"مَا","en":"what","id":"apa"},{"a":"هِيَهْ","en":"it is","id":"itu"}]},{"n":11,"key":"101:11","arabic":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةٌۢ","page":600,"juz":30,"en":"It is a Fire, intensely hot.","id":"(Yaitu) api yang sangat panas.","words":[{"a":"نَارٌ","en":"A Fire","id":"api"},{"a":"حَامِيَةٌۢ","en":"intensely hot","id":"sangat panas"}]}]}